This paper discusses the architecture and infrastructure of a digital library, which involves topics related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of metadata and rights management services, which are relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper mentions the inclusion of technology education, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET).
